data.description: Nestled in the heart of the Hood River valley, this exceptional property invites you to experience the epitome of refined living while taking in the breathtaking vistas of both Mt. Hood and Mt. Adams. The main house, spanning two levels, has been thoughtfully designed to capture the essence of its surroundings and offer unparalleled comfort.Step inside the main house and be greeted by the allure of spacious interiors, where a large great room boasts soaring ceilings, expansive windows that frame the stunning double mountain views, and an inviting fireplace that becomes the focal point of gatherings. The kitchen and dining area, adorned with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, blend style with functionality, making culinary endeavors a delight.A primary bedroom on the main level leads to a balcony, offering a private retreat with unparalleled views. An additional versatile room on this level provides endless possibilities for customization to suit your needs.Venture to the upper level, where a spacious bedroom with an en-suite bathroom offers a comfortable oasis. A cozy loft area completes this level, providing a space for relaxation and contemplation.Now, descend to the lower level, where you'll discover an exceptional opportunity for income potential or additional accommodations. A self-contained 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment with its own entrance offers versatility as a guest retreat, a rental unit, or a personal haven for extended family.The property is not only defined by its exquisite main house but also features a fenced backyard, a private road, and room for RV parking, all seamlessly complementing the allure of Hood River living.With its captivating double mountain views, income potential from the lower level apartment, and the perfect balance of natural beauty and contemporary living, this property embodies the Hood River lifestyle you've been dreaming of.
